Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让小葵看到富士山这个计划完美成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额 我觉得是成功了 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以三增峠的山顶为目标继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离山顶还有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.63,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(524,416)}下山之后的乐趣!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是屏风岩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增峠也是攀爬的名地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵要不要试试看？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前大家一起练习过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟攀岩完全不同啊 我还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了屏风岩就是山顶了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后冲刺了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转眼大片美好的景色就展现在我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前进 前进 前进 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点 再前进一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 已经看得到山顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠自己的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么充实的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么空气这么清新呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是… 这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 枫 心夏 好漂亮 景色好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 我还是第一次见到小葵这么能闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我笑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你的手停住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好吃饭补充能量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重要的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去也要走很多路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 要多吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐的时间结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有开始就会有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登上山就还要下山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拥有更多这样的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山的时候要让它稍微长一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握的方式也变了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快下山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山下面有温泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的时候有招牌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是真的 在车站附近有温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的时候泡上一会也是登山的乐趣之一呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉 温泉 温泉 温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉 要大家一起泡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不进去泡温泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是露天的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中学修学旅行时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大家睡着的时候才偷偷进去泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山会容易控制不了速度 很可怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是想温泉的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得集中精神下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫 下山该怎么走才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山的话 比起体力还是更靠经验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺着地势 顺势下山更好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样 顺势而下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果只能小心地走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为下山容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是来的时候很可怕的路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为走过一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不觉得可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么呢 感觉好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有长凳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在长凳上休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…膝盖好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且相当疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 你的膝盖还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很疼 脚承受了很大的负担呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点哦 在这种平坦的地方是会受伤的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走过了艰险的地方 放心的一瞬间是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我要好好集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膝盖好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啊 我在膝盖上绑了护具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜的就行 买一个会轻松很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松 轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山之前就告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还得走多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山的时候没注意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个现在都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 熊先生 有缘再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 马上就到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走过登山道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要走很长的路才能到车站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的时候还说柏油路好走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到回去的时候竟然这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑身是汗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔倒全身都是泥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上感觉糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉 温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(454,50)}害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定不错呢 我想快点进去泡温泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是温泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚疼 疼 疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉 温泉 温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡澡不可以裹着毛巾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在进浴池之前得要洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉 温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来 果然还是害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫 你的胸部很大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部大也没有好事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍运动 看起来就胖 还重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵也过来这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是害羞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才不喜欢和大家一起泡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天走了很多路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 2号线出发的假日快速富士山号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途径大宫 前往小山方向 现在发车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有座位真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样去新秋津 换乘西武池袋线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要2个小时左右呢
